flow 需求计划填报 {
  @base http://10.0.0.5:8080
  @source requirement-plan-filing_runtimeflow_api_requests.txt + requirement-plan-filing_playwright_records.ts
  @capturedAt 2026-06-09T10:22:00Z

  # 一条完整业务闭环：列表查询 → 新增 → 详情 → 删除

  [计划列表] @route=#/req/plan/list @component=src/views/req/plan/PlanList.vue
    打开列表 → 查询
    → GET /api/requirement/plan/list?page=1&size=20   @backend=PlanController.list → PlanService.page
      resp {total:int, list:[{id:int, name:str, status:enum(draft|submitted)}]}   ~real: total=12

  [计划新增] @route=#/req/plan/new @component=src/views/req/plan/PlanForm.vue
    点击新增 → 填写名称 → 选择费用来源 → 提交
    → GET /api/budget/source/list                     @backend=BudgetController.sources
      resp [{code:str, name:str}]                      ~real: 9 项
    → POST /api/requirement/plan/save                 @backend=PlanController.save → PlanService.create
      req  {name:str, budgetSource:str, items:[{name:str, qty:int}]}   ~inferred: items 单样本
      resp {id:int, status="draft"}

  [计划详情] @route=#/req/plan/detail/:id @component=src/views/req/plan/PlanDetail.vue
    点击行 → 查看详情
    → GET /api/requirement/plan/detail?id=123         @backend=PlanController.detail
      resp {id:int, name:str, items:[...], status:str}

  [计划列表] (返回并删除)
    点击删除 → 确认
    → DELETE /api/requirement/plan/123                @backend=PlanController.remove → PlanService.delete
      resp {success:bool}                              ~real: success=true
    → GET /api/requirement/plan/list?page=1&size=20   (同上, 复用契约; 删除后自动刷新)
}
